{"tid":2264793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又係中國】「LOL mobile」公測，中國玩家入侵日服掀駡戰","createTime":"2020-10-31T02:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T11:35:58.000Z","uid":25178,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b27a0c98f9010dd47f9bb40837c86fdf9388fe0","tid":2264793,"uid":25178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T02:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sk0hmU6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSk0hmU6.png&h=3b33a707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tagosaku15/status/1321355786010775553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftagosaku15%2Fstatus%2F1321355786010775553&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=dc103eb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftagosaku15%2Fstatus%2F1321355786010775553&h=0f5bd89c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tagosaku15/status/1321355786010775553</a><br />\n<strong>《英雄聯盟 激鬥峽谷》日本、東南亞開測，中國玩家入侵又掀兩國網友罵戰</strong><br />\n<br />\n《英雄聯盟 激鬥峽谷》原訂在 28 日於日本、東南亞開啟公開測試，不過在開始 OB 後，馬上就被大量玩家擠爆，逼的官方出面道歉並進入維修。<br />\n<br />\n雖然開機後，已經擠進登入的玩家可以正常遊玩，但還是很多人卡在登入錯誤的狀況，而且時好時壞，官方也數次發出維修公告。即便官方有鎖區域 IP，依然擋不住很多使用 VPN 的其他亞洲玩家－特別是<span class=\"red\">來自中國的玩家人數眾多</span>。<br />\n<br />\n日本 Riot 也按照一般慣例，在維修時都會在推特公告並跟玩家們道歉，但<span class=\"red\">沒想到這次卻跑來了許多中國玩家以中文留言</span>，有的玩家催促官方快修好，也有人直接嘲諷官方到底行不行，也有些人表示「感覺是因為國人所以擠爆了」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oD2ohrR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoD2ohrR.jpg&h=c29be533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VjnrZFa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjnrZFa.jpg&h=c6091086&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n日本玩家發現有許多中國玩家跑來留言後，自然覺得這是一種「侵門踏戶」的行為－<span class=\"red\">畢竟公測區域本來就不包含中國，跨區來玩已經理虧還來開嘲諷</span>，很快的就在《英雄聯盟 激鬥峽谷》的官方推特下戰起來，讓官方社群人員還得出來洗地，刪除部分留言。<br />\n<br />\n此事效應也逐漸在推特發酵，前陣子 Vtuber 的事件隨著桐生可可復出後，由於小粉紅持續出征，其實還尚未完全平息，現在又碰上了這樁《英雄聯盟》事件，只讓兩邊的網路鄉民彼此越發仇視。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/45370/league-of-legends-wild-rift-china-player-make-the-server-down\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F45370%2Fleague-of-legends-wild-rift-china-player-make-the-server-down&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=7b70ae22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/45370/league-of-legends-wild-rift-china-player-make-the-server-down</a>"},{"pid":"5c49d306dc29dac498830cdab369fbe4a7dbbd88","tid":2264793,"uid":127425,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:02:54.000Z","msg":"小日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時開服比我國"},{"pid":"c20580346c7a5bf6f9b2391c4486174c8c229315","tid":2264793,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:04:02.000Z","msg":"台服係大哥大代理<br />\n唔知有無搞BAN IP呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1e36352a4a65cbf828c5a6c37b5901dbf0ee88","tid":2264793,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:08:18.000Z","msg":"真係抵人地鎖ip<br />\n岩啦 禁埋香港<br />\n共享大灣區繁榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03c996943447e26a5739bb2e2bcd5ff89c118a6","tid":2264793,"uid":180851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:08:34.000Z","msg":"蝗禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a8f37dab4a2a311dbb4a1a7fbf77adf06bec70","tid":2264793,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:12:23.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"green\"><span class=\"xx-large\">蚹蛤蟈蜻</span></span>"},{"pid":"679f1cdbed0e6f7813b9a09baf5c6684703bdc61","tid":2